HEADWORD: Clothier
<hw>Cloth"ier</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
makes cloths; one who dresses or fulls cloth.</def>
<rj><au>Hayward.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who sells cloth or clothes, or who makes and
sells clothes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clothing</ent>⟦br⟧
